q.xml 

you can import (copy and paste) this directly to modmine 

http://intermine.modencode.org/release-32/importQueries.do?query_builder=yes

(edit in case and) run the query

from the result table you can see/download the code for the webservice ('code' drop down above the pagination)

this is done already for you in the other files

code.py
code.pl
code.rb
code.java
code.js

Note: for the service request to be release indipendent, use query instead of release-32 (it will use the latest release)

e.g.
service = Service.new("http://intermine.modencode.org/release-32")
becomes
service = Service.new("http://intermine.modencode.org/query")
